dcterms:creator: Raghunathan Ramakrishnan, Pavlo O Dral, Matthias Rupp, O Anatole Von Lilienfeld
dcterms:description: A dataset containing approximately 130,000 molecules made up of H, C, N, O, and F atoms, along with 13 quantum chemical properties for each molecule, calculated using Gaussian 09 at the B3LYP/6-31G(2df,p) level of theory.
dcterms:title: QM9 Dataset

dcterms:creator: Raghunathan Ramakrishnan, Pavlo O Dral, Matthias Rupp, O Anatole Von Lilienfeld
dcterms:description: A subset of the QM9 dataset containing molecules with fewer than 14 atoms, used for training and evaluation.
dcterms:title: QM9under14atoms

dcterms:creator: Raghunathan Ramakrishnan, Pavlo O Dral, Matthias Rupp, O Anatole Von Lilienfeld
dcterms:description: A subset of the QM9 dataset containing molecules with more than 15 atoms, used for extrapolation evaluation.
dcterms:title: QM9over15atoms
